\( H(s) = \displaystyle \frac{Y(s)}{X(s)} \) = \{ ans_rule(15) \}
$PAR
(b) If \( x(t) = \sin($omega t) \), then \( y(t) = A \sin($omega t + \phi) \) where:
$PAR
\( A = \) \{ ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
\( \phi = \) \{ ans_rule(25) \}

END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

